metadata.name: Timeless Love
metadata.description:
Timeless love - Edition

✤ ✤ ✤

This collaboration piece created between Mannay and Terrell Jones was created for the HER series anniversary.

“I shall not speak, I shall think about nothing: But endless love will mount in my soul; And I shall travel far, very far, like a gipsy, Through the countryside – as happy as if I were with a woman.” A.R.

It's about love, about her, about us, about you and about time. It's about a journey, a visual story. She's a poppy. She's rooted in me.

✤ ✤ ✤

Artwork & music composition by Mannay & Terrell Jones (2023)
